Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憧～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公交呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有3分钟才到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小稳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  转校生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是穿得这么可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这在东京很流行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的爱好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在东京也是属于极少数派的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  差不多请不要再用「转校生」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有「可爱小姐」之类的称呼可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那么  叫你什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们成为朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
